OL,3,CColdplay and FIFA working on first
OL,4,Cever World Cup final halftime show
OL,6,FColdplay singer Chris Martin is
OL,7,Fworking with FIFA to curate the first
OL,8,Fever Super Bowl-style halftime show at
OL,9,Fthe football World Cup final next year.
OL,11,FFIFA is also staging what its
OL,12,Fpresident Gianni Infantino called a
OL,13,F"takeover" of Times Square for the
OL,14,Ffinal weekend of the tournament, which
OL,15,Fwill be co-hosted by the US, Mexico
OL,16,Fand Canada.
OL,18,FPosting on Instagram, Infantino wrote:
OL,19,F"I can confirm the first ever half-
OL,20,Ftime show at a FIFA World Cup final,"
